<h2>Taking the Fear Out of Islam</h2><p class="eventtime">Every Wednesday, from 07/10/2013 to 07/31/2013<span class='event-sep'>, </span><span class="eventTime"> 7:00 PM -  8:30 PM</span></p><br/><b>Group:</b> Women's Ministry, Men's Ministry, Young Adult Ministry, Life Learning</p><p><b>Coordinator:</b> Life Learning @ PCC</p><!-- Life Learning @ PCC --><div id="text"><h2>Taking the Fear Out of Islam</h2>
<h4>Cross Cultural Missions Training Seminar</h4>
<p><strong>July 10, 17, 24, 31</strong><br /> <strong>Wednesdays, 7:00 to 8:30 PM</strong><br /> <strong>With Samuel Hakim, President of Redeeming the Nations Ministry</strong></p>
<p><a href="https://secure.accessacs.com/access/eventlogin.aspx?id=fx1QmbWhp1ISbeQycSXQHQ==&amp;site=1233&amp;ReturnUrl=events%2fwz_people.aspx&amp;ChurchID=3183&amp;EventID=49899&amp;sn=1233" class="button">Register Today</a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.pcctoday.com/article/pastor-ray-noah-what-god-has-told-me/">This workshop is in response to Pastor Ray Noah's, "God gave me <em>Four Calls to Action</em> for Portland Christian Center this year..."</a></p>
<p>The Muslim Community is experiencing growth in the Greater Portland Area and the unknown can be scary for an unprepared Christian. This powerful summer seminar will equip you with the tools to understand and engage this growing community as a vibrant follower of Christ.</p>
<p>Topics include:</p>
<ul>
<li>Islam, Challenge or Opportunity?</li>
<li>How is our community being impacted?</li>
<li>What is the history of Islam?</li>
<li>What are the beliefs and practices of the Islamic religion?</li>
<li>What are the similarities and differences of Christianity and Islam?</li>
<li>Culture! Do&rsquo;s and Don&rsquo;ts</li>
<li>How do you share the love of Jesus with Islams?</li>
<li>Using the tools you have learned to reach other cross-cultural groups</li>
<li>Love vs. Fear, what should it be?</li>
</ul></div>